elements.text:
Disk and storage monitoring ➡️ Prometheus approach could be enough
* Process list per host ➡️ Don’t think we really need that; not of much value in k8s anyhow
* OOM detection ➡️ not possible AFAIK without an agent on the node
* Host metrics ➡️ Prometheus approach could be enough
* Host properties and (VM-) topology ➡️ not possible AFAIK without an agent on the node
* Container to container network monitoring ➡️ not possible without an agent on the node
* Container metrics ➡️ Prometheus would be enough
* PG/service detection based on host groups/configs ➡️ alternative approach needed (anyhow)

writes some tracing files
for container injection
